{"tid":1477981,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］屯門譚仔有新菜式","createTime":"2019-08-16T10:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T10:42:32.000Z","uid":139225,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"24769de6afc64d08e2c9eb77803684195a7fb0cb","tid":1477981,"uid":139225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"之前已經有巴絲話呢間野有老鼠直行直過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日臥薪嘗膽上刀山<br />\n點知就一擊即中<br />\n係碗米線發現呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地問譚仔姐姐<br />\n佢就話係芽菜殘渣 然後笑笑口咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話有需要換過一碗<br />\n但佢語氣態度完全唔覺有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能佢食慣屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就覺得似肥牛渣<br />\n但譚仔又冇肥牛<br />\n不如集思廣益一下<br />\n到底呢個係乜野黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fW8Qux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fW8Qux.jpg&h=65022827&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6efcee69a75a453d4445ebffc48dc0690f2387f4","tid":1477981,"uid":308470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"一定就知係肥牛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁衛生既"}]}